text: I REALLY hope that even after the NCT 2020 promotions we still get all this great content from all the sub-units coming together (because I love seeing their interactions!!). I understand if WayV or NCT 127 for example is promoting separately as a group but just in terms of the content it's... literally the sweetest and most lovely. And yes it's expected that Xiaojun and Hendery are a little quieter. I can understand because they were only promoting with WayV until NCT 2020 came out. This is a great opportunity for the WayV guys to show how they are just as much 'NCT' as NCT 127/NCT U/NCT DREAM and not just the 'other' group that promotes mostly in China (rather, as a sub-unit that promotes internationally -including Korea). So imo yes... I can see why they are being careful. NCT members couldn't even mention them until recently. So this really makes me happy that they can interact and be apart of NCT fully, as they should.
author: Meaghen

Waseh idenya bagus dalam konten ini, dengan begini mereka akan akrab seperti keluarga satu sama lain 🤗

Ditunggu konten selanjutnya dari Sun (#Haechan) & Moon (kak #Taeil) ini, maybe bisa 00Liner yg paling banyak ato Liner yang paling hmmmm paling di idolakan dari semua member NCT maybe 95Liner ?? Wah tidak sabar menunggu ❤
Dalam konten ini terdengar beberapa suara member, hmmmm aku sangat kagum dengan kak Kim #Doyoung yang slalu support adik-adiknya patut dicontoh 👍
Untuk #Lucas #Mark #Xiaojun #Hendery semoga kalian kompak slalu dalam line mu, dan juga bisa membuat suasana di NCT menyenangkan sepanjang waktu 🤗
Dan untuk semua member jaga kesehatan kalian juga semangat terus agar bisa mencapai impian kalian bersama-sama serta terimakasih kerja keras kalian ❤
